tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE AI_Digital_Art (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  image_url TEXT,
  training_data TEXT,
  model_output TEXT,
  created_at TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE AI_Datasets (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    dataset_name VARCHAR(255),
    data_type VARCHAR(50),
    creation_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE AI_Models (
    model_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_name VARCHAR(255),
    model_type VARCHAR(50),
    accuracy FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE Training_Examples (
    example_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    dataset_id INT,
    model_id INT,
    feature_vector JSONB,
    label VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE Model_Predictions (
    prediction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_id INT,
    input_vector JSONB,
    predicted_output VARCHAR(50),
    confidence FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE Training_Logs (
    log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_id INT,
    epoch_number INT,
    loss FLOAT,
    accuracy FLOAT
)
